---
import "@fontsource/roboto";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import SectionHeading from "../components/SectionHeading.astro";
import LayoutDefault from "../layouts/LayoutDefault.astro";
---

<LayoutDefault>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center my-20">
    <img src="/logo.svg" alt="NixCon 2023" class="w-72" />
    <p class="mt-4 text-5xl font-bold text-gray-600 font-behrensschrift">
      Darmstadt 2023
    </p>
    <p class="text-3xl font-behrensschrift font-bold text-gray-600">
      September 08 - 10
    </p>
  </div>

  <Section>
    <SectionHeading>About</SectionHeading>
    <p>
      NixCon is a community-oriented conference for contributors and users of
      Nix and NixOS. It's about sharing experiences, inspiring people and
      discussing future development.
    </p>
    <p>
      We would like to learn about how you use Nix and NixOS in your
      organization and what you are currently working on.
    </p>
    <p>
      The growth of NixOS as a project brings its own challenges and we would
      like to know how you think the user experience can be improved and how
      NixOS can be scaled.
    </p>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <SectionHeading>Location</SectionHeading>
    <a
      href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/26931271#map=19/49.87717/8.65750&layers=N"
      rel="external"
    >
      <b class="inline-block mb-2">TU-Darmstadt, S1|05 Machinenhaus</b><br />
      Magdalenenstr. 12<br />
      64289 Darmstadt,<br />
      Germany
    </a>
  </Section>
</LayoutDefault>
